use-candidate-congressman-dan-lipinski/ |title=Pro-Israel America Endorses Congressman Lipinski}}</ref>\n* [[International Association of Sheet Metal, Air, Rail and Transportation Workers]] <ref name= \"3rd District\" />\n* [[Susan B. Anthony List]] <ref name = \"Pro-life Group Supports Lipinski\">{{Cite web | url=https://www.catholicnewsagency.com/news/pro-life-group-will-support-pro-life-democrat-lipinski-in-2020-31426 |title= Pro-Life Group Supports Lipinski}}</ref>\n* [[Transportation Communications Union]] / [[International Association of Machinists and Aerospace Workers]] <ref name= \"3rd District\" />\n* Will & Grundy Counties Building Trades Council <ref name= \"3rd District\" />\n; Individuals\n* [[James Zogby]]. Founder and President of the [[Arab American Institute]] and former member of the executive committee of the [[Democratic National Committee]] <ref>{{Cite web | url= https://www.democratsforlife.org/index.php/about-us/advisory-boards |title=Former DNC Executive Committee Member Zogby Endorses Congressman Lipinski}}</ref>\n}}\n\n{{Endorsements box\n| title = Marie Newman\n| width= 68em\n| list =\n;U.S. Executive Branch Officials\n*[[Julian Castro]], Former Secretary of Housing and Urban Development; Former Mayor of San Antonio, Texas; former candidate in the [[2020 Democratic Party presidential primaries]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/JulianCastro/status/1230559161282228231|title=I\u2019m thrilled to endorse @Marie4Congress in Illinois 3rd Congressional District. Instead of playing Washington politics, Marie will be a representative that the people of Illinois can trust to put them and their families first. Join me in supporting her|first=Juli\u00e1n|last=Castro|date=February 20, 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/Marie4Congress/status/1230559511707971587|title=I am truly honored to receive Sec. @JulianCastro\u2019s endorsement. We are going to put immigrants first, we are going to put working families first, we are going 