vableworld.org/meet-the-candidates/house-candidates/betsy-londrigan-for-house-il-13/|website=Council for a Livable World}}</ref>\n*[[EMILY's List]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://emilyslist.org/candidates/betsy-dirksen-londrigan-20|title=Betsy Dirksen Londrigan|website=emilyslist.org|accessdate=January 12, 2020}}</ref>\n* [[End Citizens United]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Muller |first1=Tiffany |title=End Citizens United Endorses Betsy Dirksen Londrigan for IL-13|url=https://endcitizensunited.org/press-releases/end-citizens-united-endorses-betsy-dirksen-londrigan-il-13/ |website=End Citizens United |date=June 26, 2019}}</ref>\n*Illinois Nurses Association PAC<Ref>https://twitter.com/BetsyforIL</ref>\n* [[J Street PAC]]<ref name=\"JStreet\" />\n* [[League of Conservation Voters]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://twitter.com/LCVoters/status/1192504427246166023?s=20|title=LCVAF is excited to endorse @BetsyforIL to represent #IL13. Dirksen Londrigan is committed to fighting to ensure that all of our children have clean water to drink, clean air to breathe and public lands to explore and we need her leadership in Congress.|date=7 November 2019}}</ref>\n* [[NARAL Pro-Choice America]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Hogue |first=Ilyse |title=NARAL Pro-Choice America Endorses Betsy Dirksen Londrigan for Congress|url=https://www.prochoiceamerica.org/2019/09/03/naral-londrigan-endorsement/ |website=NARAL Pro-Choice America |date=September 3, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[New Democrat Coalition]] <ref>{{cite web |title= Frontier - NewDem Action Fund|url=http://newdemactionfund.com/frontier|website=NewDem Action Fund}}</ref>\n* [[Planned Parenthood Action Fund]]<ref name=\"PP\" />\n}}\n{{Endorsements box\n| title = Stefanie Smith\n| width= 68em\n| list =\n;Organizations\n* [[Democratic Socialists of America]] - [[Central Illinois]] chapter<ref name=StefanieSmithEndorsements>{{cite web|url=https://www.stefanie2020.com/endorsements|title=Endorsements|work=Stefanie Smith: US Congress in IL-13|accessdate=February 3, 2