upremacist, and nominee for Illinois's 3rd congressional district in [[2018 United States House of Representatives elections in Illinois#District 3|2018]]<ref name=\"Jones\">{{cite web |last1=Sweet |first1=Lynn |title=Holocaust denier, activist anti-Semite files again for Chicago-area House seat |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/politics/2019/12/2/20992050/holocaust-denier-arthur-jones-candidate-republican-primary-3rd-congressional-district |website=Chicago Sun Times |accessdate=December 3, 2019 |date=December 2, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Sweet|first1=Lynn|last2=Main|first2=Frank|url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/news/holocaust-denier-arthur-jones-republican-3rd-congressional-district-lipinski-newman/|title=Holocaust denier poised to claim GOP nomination in Illinois race for Congress|accessdate=February 5, 2018|work=Chicago Sun-Times|date=February 4, 2018}}</ref>\n*Catherine O'Shea, real estate broker<ref name=\"Jones\"/>\n\n=====Endorsements=====\n{{Endorsements box\n| title = Mike Fricilone\n| width= 68em\n| list =\n;Illinois Republican Party Leaders\n*Republican Senate Leader [[Bill Brady (politician)|Bill Brady]]<ref name=\"capitolfax.com\">{{Cite web|url=https://capitolfax.com/2020/02/05/rate-the-first-marie-newman-tv-ad/|title=Capitol Fax.com - Your Illinois News Radar \u00bb Rate the first Marie Newman TV ad|website=capitolfax.com}}</ref>\n*Republican House Leader [[Jim Durkin]]<ref name=\"capitolfax.com\" />\n*Cook County Republican Chairman Sean M. Morrison<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/CookCountyGOP/status/1201637573984243717|title=Cook County GOP Chairman @SeanMMorrison blasts the congressional candidacy of \u2018monster\u2019 Arthur Jones and urges Republican voters in the 3rd Congressional District to back Will County Board Member Mike Fricilone - a principled, conservative Republican - candidate for Congress.pic.twitter.com/wso0bAhzFi|first=Cook County|last=GOP|date=December 2, 2019}}</ref>\n*Will County Republican Chairman George Pear