m/ Brad Schneider (D) for Congress]\n* [https://www.valforcongress.com/ Valerie Ramirez-Mukherjee (R) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 11th district candidates\n* [https://billfoster.com/ Bill Foster (D) for Congress]\n* [https://www.ricklaib2020.com/ Rick Laib (R) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 12th district candidates\n* [http://bostforcongress.com/ Mike Bost (R) for Congress]\n* [https://lenziforcongress.org/ Ray Lenzi (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 13th district candidates\n* [https://electrodney.com/ Rodney Davis (R) for Congress]\n* [https://www.betsydirksenlondrigan.com/ Betsy Dirksen Londrigan (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 14th district candidates\n* [https://jim2020.com/ Jim Oberweis (R) for Congress]\n* [https://www.underwoodforcongress.com/ Lauren Underwood (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 15th district candidates\n* [https://www.marymillerforcongress.com/ Mary Miller (R) for Congress]\n* [https://weaverforillinois.com/ Erika Weaver (D) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 16th district candidates\n* [https://www.daniforillinois.com/ Dani Brzozowski (D) for Congress]\n* [https://www.electadam.com/ Adam Kinzinger (R) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 17th district candidates\n* [https://www.cheribustos.com/ Cheri Bustos (D) for Congress]\n* [https://www.estherforcongress.com/ Esther Joy King (R) for Congress]\n\n;Official campaign websites for 18th district candidates\n* [https://www.lahoodforcongress.com/ Darin LaHood (R) for Congress]\n{{col-end}}\n{{2020 United States elections}}\n\n[[Category:2020 United States House of Representatives elections|Illinois]]\n[[Category:United States House of Representatives elections in Illinois|2020]]\n[[Category:2020 Illinois elections|House]]\n", "name_user": "Starklinson", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eEndorsements", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2020_United_States_House_of_